  "texts": [
    "rDPO Chowdhury et al. (2024) propose robust DPO (rDPO) to address concerns about the noisy data.",
    "It seeks to de-bias the effect of noise on average by equating logits with noise and logits without noise.",
    "Derived based on the cDPO approach and the de-biasing assumption, the rDPO loss L rDPO is",
    "While this loss can be seen as an unbiased estimator of L DPO, ϵ value should be tuned through crossvalidation since it is unknown in practice.",
    "Preference Datasets Popular preference datasets include Anthropic-HH (Bai et al., 2022a) and UltraFeedback (Cui et al., 2023)."
  ]
}